... maybe what that means is that although focus items do not stack with AA crits, maybe they do stack with innate crits? I use ISS quite a bit and the best I've ever done is 2587 on an innate crit (with 23% dmg focus and Iceflame).<br>
<br>
1200 + 50% innate crit + 53% focus = 2436 max damage<br>
1200 + 55% innate crit + 53% focus = 2496 max damage<br>
(1200 + 50% innate crit) + 53% focus = 2754 max damage<br>
<br>
I know I did NOT have Rizlona's on me when I got that crit (the screenshot shows me as soloing at the time).<br>
