<br>
base * Innate(1.5) *ID3(1.2) = base *1.8.<br>
base * Innate(1.5) *focus23%(1.23) * Iceflame(1.3) = 2.295*base<br>
<br>
Ice Comet Max innate crit (50%) with id3 = 1.8*1120 = 2016<br>
Ice Spear max innate crit (50%) with id3 = 1.8*1200 = 2160<br>
Ice Spear max innate crit (50%) with 23% focus and iceflame 30% = 2.295 * 1200 = 2754<br>
<br>
However focus does not stack with AA crits as per my previous post, linking a patch message.  Though since it doesn't stack with AA Crits it probably was not intended to stack with innate crits either.<br>
